data.description: Welcome to this spacious home in the picturesque town of Perry, Georgia! Boasting an expansive 3,086 square feet of living space, this residence offers an abundance of room for comfortable living. Built in 2018, it showcases modern features and practical layout.  Upon entering through the front door, you'll be greeted by a tasteful formal dining room and a versatile secondary living area that can easily adapt to your needs – whether it's a home office, playroom, or a cozy reading nook. The inviting living room seamlessly connects to the well-appointed kitchen, complete with a convenient breakfast bar, breakfast area, pantry, all major kitchen appliances, and elegant granite countertops.  On the main level, you'll discover a bedroom and a full bathroom, providing an ideal space for in-laws or overnight guests, ensuring everyone feels right at home. As you ascend the stairs, you'll find four additional bedrooms, including the generously sized Owner's Suite. This luxurious retreat features a separate sitting area and a private bathroom, creating a serene escape within your own home. Plus, the laundry room is conveniently located on the second level, ensuring easy access from the bedrooms.  Stepping outside, you'll be delighted by the vast privacy fenced backyard, offering ample space for entertaining, playing with pets, or simply basking in the outdoors. Situated just a stone's throw away from local schools, I-75, and Downtown Perry, this home's location is incredibly convenient for all your daily needs and adventures.  Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautiful Perry home your own – with its spacious interior, modern amenities, and prime location, it's the perfect place to create lasting memories and enjoy a comfortable lifestyle.
